WEBVTT

00:00:26.624 --> 00:00:31.549
Po si fillim, do t'ju tregoj nje histori
nga Z. Richard Messina,

00:00:31.573 --> 00:00:34.702
i cili eshte miku im dhe
drejtor i nje shkolle fillore.

00:00:35.266 --> 00:00:36.827
Nje dite mori nje telefonate.

00:00:39.279 --> 00:00:40.430
Telefonuesi tha,

00:00:40.454 --> 00:00:44.336
"Z. Messina, djali im Johnny 
nuk do te vije ne shkolle sot

00:00:44.360 --> 00:00:45.823
sepse eshte semure."

00:00:46.498 --> 00:00:48.234
Z. Messina pyeti,

00:00:48.258 --> 00:00:50.272
"Me ke po flas ju lutem?"

00:00:50.788 --> 00:00:52.278
Dhe telefonuesi tha,

00:00:52.302 --> 00:00:53.967
"Une jam babai im."

00:00:53.991 --> 00:00:56.778
(Te qeshura)

00:00:58.227 --> 00:00:59.909
Keshtu kjo histori--

00:00:59.933 --> 00:01:01.465
(Te qeshura)